Supported update surface: definedTags,
description, displayName, freeformTags
Reject before mutate: force-new fields
compartmentId, systemTags
Lookup filters: compartmentId,
displayName
Lookup matching: exact compartmentId
plus displayName unique match in ACTIVE,
CREATING, or UPDATING; empty displayName
skips lookup and duplicate matches fail
end note
opt force-new or conflicting drift is detected
ServiceManager --> BaseReconciler: reject before OCI mutation
end
opt supported mutable drift is detected
ServiceManager -> OCI: Apply\nChangeDashboardGroupCompartment,\nUpdateDashboardGroup only for\nmutable fields definedTags,\ndescription, displayName,\nfreeformTags
loop update pending UPDATING
ServiceManager -> OCI: GetDashboardGroup
end
end
ServiceManager -> OCI: run helper hooks\ncreate=tfresource.CreateResource;\nupdate=tfresource.UpdateResource;\ndelete=tfresource.DeleteResource
